&lt;li&gt;Install the MantaHQ SDK.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement pagination using the provided example component.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Follow the MantaHQ documentation for setup:&lt;/p&gt;

